      <title>贝莱德预计日本央行将维持利率较长时间，利好股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/blackrock-expects-boj-to-hold-rates-for-longer-in-boon-to-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司对日本股市持有高度信心的投资观点，该公司认为，日本央行可能会在较长时间内维持利率不变，以提振日本股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/blackrock-expects-boj-to-hold-rates-for-longer-in-boon-to-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
